tags.description:
Park includes a Pickleball court, a grass lawn, a bike rack, three benches, a DogiPot dispenser, a trash can.
The park is open to Highlands residents only. Car parking is highly discouraged. However, biking, walking, skating, etc. is greatly encouraged
tags.name: Highlands Pickleball Park
